---
title: Harissa Spiced Butter Bean and Cavolo Nero Stew with Feta Crumb, Pea Shoot Salad and Garlic Ciabatta
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Harissa Spiced Butter Bean and Cavolo Nero Stew in just 20 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/harissa-spiced-butter-bean-and-cavolo-nero-stew-69764e26-75ce4b6d.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/harissa-spiced-butter-bean-and-cavolo-nero-stew-6138c27cef9fbd76413ea07e-6126e51f.pdf
